## 🚀 Running the Services

### App Service
```bash
cd player-service-app
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

### Model Service (Docker)
```bash
cd player-service-model
docker build -t a4a_model .
docker run -d -p 8657:8657 a4a_model
```
